title: Two LP Gas tankers to reach SL next week
body_lines: COLOMBO (News 1st); Litro gas said that two gas shipments will arrive in the country next week.
The Chairman of Litro gas Eng. Vijitha Herath said 50,000 domestic gas cylinders will be distributed to the market on Friday (20).
